data.description: Have a seat on your front porch overlooking the peaceful front yard or enjoy the privacy of a fully fenced backyard. Home interior has had some upgrades that include granite countertops and tile throughout except in front living room. The roof and decking was replaced two years ago. This sweet, quiet home sits on just under half an acre large lot with mature trees. Attached to the Florida room is a storage room.  No HOA or CDD.
